About Regal Party Rentals

Regal Party Rentals provides premium tent and party equipment rentals across the Lower Mainland and Vancouver Island. Based in Surrey (our headquarters), we primarily serve North Vancouver, Langley, Coquitlam, Metro Vancouver, and also provide extended service to Vancouver Island. Professional event solutions for weddings, corporate events, and special occasions. Family-owned and operated since 2023.

With years of experience in the BC event rental industry, we understand the unique needs of events across our diverse service areas. From intimate Surrey backyard celebrations to large-scale Vancouver corporate events, we provide exceptional service and premium equipment that makes every occasion memorable.

Our commitment to excellence, combined with our local expertise and comprehensive service coverage, makes us the trusted choice for event rentals throughout British Columbia.
